quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,105,people Noah disbelieved messengers
  26,106,Their frater Noah dictus to them vos non est righteous
  26,107,Ego est honest messenger vos
  26,108,Vos reverence DEUS obey me
  26,109,Ego non ask vos any wage My wage advenit ex Dominus universe
  26,110,Vos reverence DEUS obey me
  26,111,They dictus Quam nos believe vos potuit when malus among nos subsequentis vos
  26,112,He dictus Quam ego know quod they perfecit perfecit
  26,113,Their judgment rests unus my Dominus vos perceive
  26,114,Ego nunquam dismiss believers
  26,115,Ego est non multus than clarifying warner
  26,116,They dictus vos refrain O Noah vos stoned
  26,117,He dictus My Dominus my people disbelieved me
  26,118,Grant me victory them deliver me my company believers
  26,119,Nos delivered eum those accompanied eum loaded ark
  26,120,Tunc nos drowned others
  26,121,Hoc est lesson multus people non est believers
  26,122,multus assuredly tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful